**[1863, 10-03] Ms.A.1.2.32.52B**

GT to WLG; London {Bulk in {u}BAA{/u}, though with spelling errors.}

“You will henceforth see all changed here. The word has gone forth—the
cure has been given—the priests received its instructions from head
quarters; & for the future it will be *The United States, England* & the
*Czar*, against *Napoleon*& *Jeff Davis*—Anti-Slavery Britain and the
north against … the flesh mongers of the South and their allies in the
plain of Mexico.”


